Plymouth County, Massachusetts Plymouth County, located along the western shores of Cape Cod Bay:cite web   last = Nason   first = Elias   coauthor = George G. Varney   title = Plymouth County Massachusetts, 1890   work = Massachusetts Gazetteer   date = 1890   url = http://capecodhistory.us/Mass1890/PlymouthCo1890.htm   accessdate = 2007-04-03 
